## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="286e1-102">之前<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>可以呈现控件，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem>必须为每个控件中的项创建对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-102">Before the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control can be rendered, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem> object must be created for each item in the control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="286e1-103"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemCreated>每次引发事件，中的项<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>创建控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemCreated> event is raised every time that an item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="286e1-104">这使你能够执行自定义的例程，每当创建一个项，如将自定义内容添加到项的事件处理方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-104">This enables you to provide an event-handling method that performs a custom routine whenever an item is created, such as adding custom content to an item.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="286e1-105">同样之前,<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>可以呈现控件、 控件中的每个项必须绑定到数据源中的记录。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-105">Similarly, before the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control can be rendered, every item in the control must be bound to a record in the data source.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="286e1-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemDataBound>项时引发事件 (由表示<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem>对象) 中的数据绑定<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemDataBound> event is raised when an item (represented by a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem> object) is bound to data in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="286e1-107">这使您可以项绑定到数据，例如修改数据的值，它们显示之前执行自定义的例程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-107">This enables you to perform a custom routine whenever an item is bound to data, such as modifying the values of the data before they are displayed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="286e1-108">A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItemEventArgs>对象传递给事件处理方法，使你可以访问引发事件的项的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-108">A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItemEventArgs> object is passed to the event-handling method, which enables you to access the properties of the item that raised the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="286e1-109">若要确定正在创建哪种项目类型 （数据项、 空项或插入项），使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem.ItemType%2A>属性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="286e1-109">To determine which item type (data item, empty item, or insert item) is being created, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem.ItemType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewItem> object.</span></span>  
  
